{"tid":886964,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"日式串燒食評","createTime":"2018-11-02T13:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T10:04:24.000Z","uid":175988,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ccdb6f7bb2e278932486658464ac7cd7c3a008ab","tid":886964,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>八兆屋 @ 新城市廣場</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0EM9BPb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0EM9BPb.jpg&h=164b7b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>串燒拼盤</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即叫即燒，夠新鮮又有誠意<br />\n雞肉大蔥串燒得唔錯，雞肉微脆帶焦香，大蔥鮮甜多汁，加上惹味嘅燒汁送酒一流<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聲稱係名物嘅雞肉棒唔掂，無雞肉扎實嘅質感，好明顯加咗太多粉，又無軟骨增加層次同口感<br />\n雞翼燒過哂火，皮同肉都過韌，雪味又重，唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 行過當過吓口癮就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"ab50cf7870085c18c06364bbb43e69e8b6a02283","tid":886964,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:44:46.000Z","msg":"$$?"},{"pid":"335808fd1e6c0b53a30ad1e4bb85151dea840b2f","tid":886964,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>同場加映</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JJWHlul.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJJWHlul.jpg&h=5c98a9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>抹茶紅豆忌廉包</strong><br />\n包身過濕唔夠挺身，紅豆蓉太甜搶哂抹茶嘅香味，食食吓唔知點解仲有陣紅棗味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過抹茶忌廉本身幾高質，質地軟滑，茶味濃而唔苦澀，帶少許回甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 唔值得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"19f7d32b7fd201695afd1ae889613f51a15c1dbb","tid":886964,"uid":17598